                            To add Web Texting to your home screen on an iOS device, first open Web Texting. Then hit the share button in the bottom right corner of the screen. Scroll down on the sharing screen until you see a button labeled Add to Home Screen, then hit that button.
                        </p><p>
                            A prompt will come up, hit the Add button in the top right corner of the screen. The Accelerate Networks icon will appear on your home screen, labeled Web Texting.
                        </p><p>
                            To open the app in the future, just tap the Web Texting app on your home screen.
