                        <p>
                            To turn on notifications, first open Web Texting. Then hit the bell icon with a slash through it, indicating that notifications are disabled, in the top right corner of the screen.
                        </p><p>
                            You will be prompted to allow Web Texting to send you notifications, tap Allow. The bell icon will now appear without a slash through it, indicating that notifications are enabled.
                        </p><p> You will now be prompted when a new text message arrives.</p>
